<div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub78450_1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="概念"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">练耳</span>概念</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="1" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">练耳</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">ear training</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">即听觉训练，目的在于培养并发展对音乐的听辨能</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">力和记忆能力，从而丰富和提高其内在听觉，加深对乐</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">谱的实际理解和音响效果的想象力。在音乐院校中，它</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">和<a href="/item/%E8%A7%86%E5%94%B1" target="_blank">视唱</a>成为必修的一门基础课程。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub78450_2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="训练方法"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">练耳</span>训练方法</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="2" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">练耳的训练方法有:①听唱(模唱);②节奏敲击；③</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">听觉分析；④听写等。这几方面的训练必须与<a href="/item/%E4%B9%90%E7%90%86" target="_blank">乐理</a>、和</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">声、<a href="/item/%E5%A4%8D%E8%B0%83" target="_blank">复调</a>、<a href="/item/%E6%9B%B2%E5%BC%8F" target="_blank">曲式</a>等音乐理论知识结合进行，以达到对音</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">乐的<a href="/item/%E9%9F%B3%E7%A8%8B" target="_blank">音程</a>、<a data-lemmaid="3795" href="/item/%E8%8A%82%E5%A5%8F/3795" target="_blank">节奏</a>、<a href="/item/%E6%9B%B2%E8%B0%83" target="_blank">曲调</a>、调式、调性、<a data-lemmaid="2796" href="/item/%E8%8A%82%E6%8B%8D/2796" target="_blank">节拍</a>、<a href="/item/%E5%92%8C%E5%BC%A6" target="_blank">和弦</a>连接、</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><a href="/item/%E5%A4%9A%E5%A3%B0%E9%83%A8" target="_blank">多声部</a>织体、乐曲结构等的正确判断和记写。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">练耳可与<a href="/item/%E8%A7%86%E5%94%B1" target="_blank">视唱</a>同时结合进行，也可各自单独进行。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">所有的音乐实践活动，特别是<a href="/item/%E9%87%8D%E5%A5%8F" target="_blank">重奏</a>、重唱、合唱、乐队</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">排练、记录民歌等，对听觉能力的提高，大有裨益。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">练耳也叫做听写</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">对于新手来说是异常艰难的过程，甚至许多唱片公司的专业人士都掌握得马马虎虎。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">如果自学的话，最基础的训练是要听熟所有的<a href="/item/%E9%9F%B3%E9%98%B6" target="_blank">音阶</a>。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">先从1、3、5、·1、四个最难分辨的唱名开始分辨。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">等1、3、5、·1四个音能准确分辨了之后2、4、6就容易突破了。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">最好能有一台琴在身边。切记要多听多听多听。学音乐是脑力劳动，耳朵是第一，动嘴是第二。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":1," data-sup="1">
[1]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[1]_78450"> </a>
</div>
